{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_06_05",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 06 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "どういうこと？\nお兄ちゃん……やっぱりピアノを諦めちゃうの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?\nBig brother… are you really giving up on piano!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.666666666699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に諦めないで。本当は、お兄ちゃんだって\nピアニストになりたいんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't give up like that. You really want to be a pianist‚ too‚\ndon't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "endTime": 13.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、一緒にステージに立ってみて、感じたよ\nお兄ちゃんのピアノは人を感動させるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt it yesterday when we stood on stage together.\nYour piano playing moves people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "endTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう\nでも、やっぱりお前からの援助は受けない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nBut I still won't accept support from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8,
      "endTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……お兄さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6666666667,
      "endTime": 29.650317390799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでなん、お兄さんもう一度考え直して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Why? Brother‚ please reconsider.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8333333333,
      "endTime": 34.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 34.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃんの馬鹿！\nお兄ちゃんのピアノは世界一素敵なんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You idiot‚ big brother!\nYour piano playing is the most wonderful in the world!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6333333333,
      "endTime": 40.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、夢を諦めるなんて言わないで ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don't say you're giving up on your dream!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "endTime": 44.366666666600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro002.m4a",
      "text": "違う。勘違いしないでくれ、すみれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. Don't misunderstand‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6,
      "endTime": 48.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9,
      "endTime": 50.259183692899995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro003.m4a",
      "text": "俺はすみれからの援助は受けない、と言っただけだ\nピアニストになる夢は、もう二度と諦めない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I only said that I wouldn't accept support from you‚ Sumire.\nI'll never give up on my dream of becoming a pianist again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4666666667,
      "endTime": 60.300000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は働いて金を貯めるよ\nそして、自力でもう一度留学する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll work and save money.\nAnd then‚ I'll go study abroad again on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7,
      "endTime": 66.3333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 63.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "お、お兄ちゃん、それって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-Big brother‚ you mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5333333333,
      "endTime": 70.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 70.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro005.m4a",
      "text": "夢は与えられるものでも、ましてや諦めるものじゃない\n自らの意志と行動で掴み取るものだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dreams are not something that are given‚ nor are they something to be abandoned.\nThey are something to be seized with one's own will and actions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4666666667,
      "endTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 78.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro006.m4a",
      "text": "そこにいるお前の友達に教えられたよ\nそしてすみれ……お前にもだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your friend over there taught me that.\nAnd you too‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9,
      "endTime": 86.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 82.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6333333333,
      "endTime": 88.8593650142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro007.m4a",
      "text": "イベントで得た利益は、奥山酒造再建のためだけに使う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The profits from the event will be used solely for the reconstruction of Okuyama Brewery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0666666667,
      "endTime": 93.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 93.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro008.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、お前が自力で夢を追うように\n俺もきっと自分の力で夢を叶えてみせる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ just like you're chasing your dreams with your own strength‚\nI will surely achieve my dream with my own strength as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6666666667,
      "endTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro009.m4a",
      "text": "だからすみれ、お前も東京に戻って全力で夢を追え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So Sumire‚ you go back to Tokyo and chase your dreams with all your might.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2,
      "endTime": 108.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃん、じゃあ、またピアノを続けてくれるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big brother‚ so you'll continue playing the piano?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0333333333,
      "endTime": 115.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、またいつか、同じステージに立とうな、すみれ\nその時は、俺もプロになってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ let's stand on the same stage again someday‚ Sumire.\nI'll be a professional by then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7333333333,
      "endTime": 126.26666666659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 126.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃん！　良かったよ～～っ！\nうわあ～～～～んっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big brother! I'm so glad!\nWaaaaaaaah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4666666667,
      "endTime": 135.8369438306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 131.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-smrbro011.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、こら、人前でお前は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey‚ cut it out‚ you… in front of everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0333333333,
      "endTime": 140.4666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 140.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、お兄さん\nすみれちゃん今まで本当に頑張ってきたんです",
      "translations": {
